## Bat Configuration
## Docs: https://github.com/sharkdp/bat#configuration

# Theme (matches existing terminal/catppuccin setup)
--theme="Catppuccin Mocha"

# Display components: changes, grid, line-numbers, header
--style=changes,grid,numbers,header

# Show Git modifications context
--diff-context=3

# Wrap long lines
--wrap=never
